parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag system malfunctions
the airbag fails to deploy in an accident
the airbag sensor goes bad or corrodes
the airbag warning light stays on intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, leading to unnecessary repairs and potentially causing the airbag to fail to deploy in an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag sensor goes bad or corrodes
the airbag warning light stays on intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in an accident can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy in an accident
the airbag warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false airbag warning can cause unnecessary stress and lead to unnecessary repairs.

symptoms: The Service TPMS sensor message and TPMS warning light are illuminated
intermittent failure of the TPMS sensor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the key fob recognition system can cause inconvenience, delay, or even leave the driver stranded, as the vehicle may not recognize the key fob.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical fire hazard can cause damage to the vehicle, injury, or even death.
symptoms: The vehicle catches fire

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the stop engine toggle switch can cause inconvenience, delay, or even lead to accidents, as the driver may not be able to turn off the engine.
symptoms: The stop engine toggle switch assembly collapses into the dash panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic locks can cause inconvenience, delay, or even lead to theft or vandalism.
symptoms: The electronic locks fail to secure
allowing unauthorized access to the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration can cause accidents, loss of vehicle control, or even injury.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates
making it difficult to slow down or maintain control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause inconvenience, delay, or even leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery is replaced multiple times within a short period
with no underlying cause found.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature wear of the timing chain can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and power brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents and put the safety of vehicle occupants and others at risk.
symptoms: The check engine light illuminates
the engine stalls
the vehicle cannot exceed a certain speed (e.g.
25 mph)
error codes 08
and 19 are displayed.

symptoms: Fluid leaks
engine block deterioration
engine stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Power Reduction and Premature Timing Chain Wear

the vehicle slows down

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electronic Control Module and Computer System Failures

the system may start or stop working at any time
